word_group.brief_definition: 空置空间；空旷空间；空荡的空间

bilingual.source: But when I got there, the school was empty.
bilingual.target: 但当我到那儿时，学校是空的。

bilingual.source: The seat next to me is empty.

bilingual.target: 我们发现了一个空的鸟窝。

bilingual.source: Can you help me find an empty socket?
bilingual.target: 你能帮我找到一个空的插座吗？

bilingual.source: The cooky jar was empty when I checked.
bilingual.target: 当我检查时，饼干罐是空的。

bilingual.source: The beach was empty until the ocean tided.
bilingual.target: 海滩在海水涨潮前是空的。

bilingual.source: We found an empty cart in the supermarket.
bilingual.target: 我们在超市里找到了一个空的推车。

list.abstract: empty，英语单词，主要用作为名词、形容词、动词，作名词时意为空车；空的东西；作形容词时意为空的；无意义的；无知的；徒劳的；作及物动词时意为使失去；使......成为空的；作不及物动词时意为成为空的；流空。
《empty》是美国民谣歌手Ray LaMontagne演唱的一首歌曲，于2006年8月29日发行。收录在专辑《Till the Sun Turns Black》中，也是电影《超脱》的插曲。

yingyinNormal.en: The basket is totally empty. My God, the neighbors ate all the candy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 篮子是空的，邻居们把糖果吃掉了。

yingyinNormal.en: George, this is my secret box. It's empty. I have to find some things to put inside.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治，这是我的秘密盒子，现在还是空的，我得赶快找些东西放进这个盒子里去。

yingyinNormal.en: Night of the party, the car's empty, and a week later, the dead boy's found at the wheel.
yingyinNormal.zh: 派对当晚，车子是空的，一周后男孩的尸体就在驾驶座上。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, Sis, don't mean to complain, but this one's empty. What happened, did you run out of ideas?
yingyinNormal.zh: 妹妹，不是我抱怨，这间房是空的。怎么，点子用光了？

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, here's the Bitcoin folder. Yeah, how much is in there? It's empty. What? That's impossible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 找到比特币文件夹了。里面有多少钱？里面是空的。什么？怎么可能。

yingyinNormal.en: Where did you get empty Dove Bar wrappers?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你是上哪去弄的空巧克力棒包装纸？

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sitting here because the seat was empty.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我坐在这儿是因为这儿有个空位。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, aren't we Mr. The-Glass-ls-Half-Empty?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不是“看到杯子有一半儿空着”的人（悲观）。

yingyinNormal.en: This is too much to handle on an empty stomach.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太难以置信了。

yingyinNormal.en: And the car is empty at St James's Park Station.
yingyinNormal.zh: 到了圣詹姆斯公园，车就空了。

yingyinNormal.en: See, every known map registers it as empty desert.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所有已知地图上那里都是沙漠。

yingyinNormal.en: All those circuses back east burying an empty box.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所有这些表演，却只是葬了一口空棺。

yingyinNormal.en: The Empty Vase. Translucent beauty... To yourself.
yingyinNormal.zh: 空花瓶，半透明的美... 不要念出声。

yingyinNormal.en: Completely empty box. If you'd like to examine it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 空空如也的盒子，你们可以检查一下。

yingyinNormal.en: All right. Harry, you take the empty bishop's square.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，哈利，你站在象那个空格。

yingyinNormal.en: Wonder if there's any booze in this empty retro ville.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不知道这个复古无人镇上有没有酒。

yingyinNormal.en: "Half-empty, half-full" is an expression I have never cared for.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我一直不喜欢"不好不坏"这种表达。

yingyinNormal.en: Does that make this a glass-half-full or half-empty-type situation?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这算不算是考验人究竟是乐观还是悲观地看待这一情况？

yingyinNormal.en: As I was saying, empty box, empty cylinder, and ooh! Voila.
yingyinNormal.zh: 正如我所说，空盒子，空圆筒，然后呢，瞧啊！

yingyinNormal.en: But any time the big top was empty, I would practice on the wire.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但只要大帐棚有空档，我就练习走钢索。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Everybody wants to know how the people who will soon inhabit those <highlight>empty</highlight> office cubicles will differ from those who came before them.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 每个人都想知道，即将入住这些空办公室隔间的人与之前的人有什么不同。

examination_example.sentence: Half of them found a toy; the other half discovered the container was <highlight>empty</highlight> — and realized the tester had fooled them.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一半的人找到了一个玩具;另一半人发现容器是空的，并意识到试验员耍了他们。

examination_example.sentence: The "<highlight>empty</highlight> bottles" metaphor illustrates that people feel a pressure to make the passing time fulfilling.
examination_example.sentence_trans: “空瓶子”暗喻证明了人们在使流逝的时间更有满足感方面有压力。

empty作及物动词，表示“倒空；腾空”时，常用搭配为empty sth. out 清空某物; empty sth. out of sth. 从某物中取出某物。

examination_example.sentence: The schoolyard looked <highlight>empty</highlight> without them, so they decided to plant young trees.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 没有他们，校园显得空荡荡的，所以他们决定种些小树。

examination_example.sentence: After four weeks of rest, I walked into my <highlight>empty</highlight> classroom and turned on the lights.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 休息四周后，我走进了空荡荡的教室，打开了灯。

examination_example.sentence: Today, when I stand in that field which was once <highlight>empty</highlight>, I see trees about as tall as I am.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 今天，当我站在那片曾经空无一人的田野上时，我看到了和我一样高的树。
